  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0ddd\u0db8\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Mother dies in Homagama house fire",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A mother who was receiving treatment for injuries sustained in a fire that broke out in a downstairs room of a two storey house in the Magammana area in Homagama has died today (26), police said.",
        "The father had died while being taken to the hospital yesterday (25) and the mother, six year old and nineteen year old daughter were admitted to the hospital with burn injuries.",
        "Hospital sources say that the condition of the 19 year old daughter Kavindi Ranasinghe who was admitted to the hospital is critical.",
        "The deceased has been identified as SA Lasantha Buddhika and Nalika Devi, a married electrician residing in Magammana, Homagama.",
        "The fire broke out at around 8 pm when the deceased was in a basement room of a two-storey house with his wife, eldest daughter (19) and six-year-old daughter.",
        "The couple and their eldest daughter sustained serious burn injuries and the six-year-old daughter sustained minor injuries in the fire.",
        "Kahathuduwa Police say that a father was killed and three others including a six year old daughter were seriously injured in a fire that broke out in a basement of a two storey house in the Magammana area in Homagama.",
        "The deceased has been identified as SA Lasantha Buddhika Ranasinghe (47), a resident of Magammana, Homagama and a father of two.",
        "The victim was in a basement room with his wife (38), eldest daughter (19) and six-year-old daughter when a fire broke out at around 8 last night (26).",
        "The couple and their eldest daughter sustained serious burn injuries and the six-year-old daughter sustained minor injuries in the fire.",
        "The mother and relatives of the deceased were in the adjoining part of the house at the time of the fire and the eldest daughter who was with them had come to the room to comb her hair.",
        "The fire was put out by the residents of the area and the injured were admitted to the Homagama Base Hospital for treatment, police said.",
        "The six injured were rushed to the Borella Children's Hospital and the other three were admitted to the Colombo National Hospital. The 47 - year - old died on the spot, police said."
      ],
